  ('judicial-4d3895b1-moex-00032', 'judicial-4d3895b1', 'judicial-4d3895b1-moex-113-98c44bb8', 'sub-judicial-4d3895b1-03', NULL, 'essay', 'A國人甲與旅居A國多年之我國人乙為好友，乙陪同甲來臺旅遊。乙駕
